# push-swap-pain

Push swap tester for the "42-push-swap" project.
My solution can be found [here](https://github.com/Bluegales/42-push-swap) 

<img width="1785" alt="Screen Shot 2022-05-05 at 12 23 27 PM" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/72362902/166908513-77717110-2bb7-473c-a6bd-e54f2c607044.png">

https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/72362902/166651251-4310a0bf-09b2-4944-82c8-67ee403ca35a.mp4

### Usage
- Download or copy "pain.sh" and "pain2.sh" into the directory with your push_swap executable
- Change NBR_COUNT in the files depending on how many numbers you want to test
- Run pain.sh to get the visualization for a specific amount of numbers
- Run pain2.sh to check for multiple variations of the same number count.
